race.comment: FAIRWAY FURY (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (20.17) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has ability and can bounce back. CHAMPAGNE BLISS (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (17.81) in a Grade 5 at Taree Super Track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Bold showing expected. QUIRKY NACHO (4) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest when checked in the run and finishing second in a Grade 5 at this track (19.44). Expecting another bold showing. DEVOTIONAL (5) profiles nicely over this trip.
